Others: Tyrese Haliburton and the Pacers are heating up after a slow start to the season.
The Indiana Pacers picked up a 126-108 victory over the Phoenix Suns on January 5, 2025.
Tyrese Haliburton admitted that this is the most fun he's had on the basketball court this season.
Over the past 11 games, Haliburton is averaging 20.2 points and 9.7 assists per game, while shooting a much improved 48.1% from the floor.
